# ðŸ¤– CPA Agent Platform

**Universal, Ethics-First Agent Runtime for Cloud, Edge & Desktop**

> ðŸš€ **DEVELOPERS START HERE:** [platform/agentify/DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md](platform/agentify/DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md)
>
> ðŸ“– **Quick Start:** [core/agent_standard/QUICKSTART_COMPLETE.md](core/agent_standard/QUICKSTART_COMPLETE.md) - Create your first agent in 5 minutes
>
> ðŸ“ **Templates:** [core/agent_standard/templates/](core/agent_standard/templates/) - Ready-to-use JSON templates
>
> ðŸ¤– **AI Prompt:** See [Developer Guide](platform/agentify/DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md#ai-prompt-for-development) for AI-assisted development

The **CPA Agent Platform** is a production-ready framework for building, deploying, and managing AI agents with **guaranteed ethics compliance**, **universal deployment**, and **3 lines of code** to get started.

Built on the **Agent Standard v1** - the world's first universal agent wrapper with runtime-active ethics, desire-based health monitoring, and mandatory four-eyes principle.

